    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for the discerning driver is this BMW E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54B32 power unit. This high-revving 3.2L inline-six utilizes individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver linear power up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a limited-slip variable M differential. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement\u2014critical for maintaining chassis rigidity and torque transfer. The suspension remains tight with upgraded polyurethane bushings, ensuring the MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear geometry perform as intended. While showing minor patina consistent with its driver-focused history, the mechanical integrity is robust, offering a pure analog performance experience.",
